From: Andy Shevchenko <andriy.shevchenko@linux.intel.com>
Date: Thu, 30 Jul 2020 18:59:20 +0300
Subject: qed: Use %pM format specifier for MAC addresses
Patch-mainline: v5.9-rc1
Git-commit: b03c3bacf58fdb9774cf209a5773ae500556115f
References: jsc#SLE-15143

Convert to %pM instead of using custom code.

Signed-off-by: Andy Shevchenko <andriy.shevchenko@linux.intel.com>
Signed-off-by: David S. Miller <davem@davemloft.net>
Acked-by: Thomas Bogendoerfer <tbogendoerfer@suse.de>
---
 drivers/net/ethernet/qlogic/qed/qed_mcp.c   |    5 ++---
 drivers/net/ethernet/qlogic/qed/qed_sriov.c |    6 ++----
 2 files changed, 4 insertions(+), 7 deletions(-)

--- a/drivers/net/ethernet/qlogic/qed/qed_mcp.c
+++ b/drivers/net/ethernet/qlogic/qed/qed_mcp.c
@@ -2518,11 +2518,10 @@ int qed_mcp_fill_shmem_func_info(struct
 	}
 
 	DP_VERBOSE(p_hwfn, (QED_MSG_SP | NETIF_MSG_IFUP),
